]}},{"entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":255,"end":260,"tag":"News"}],"urls":[{"start":261,"end":284,"url":"https://t.co/z61yfnN3U4","expanded_url":"https://x.com/gdubon007/status/2037633244963737649/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/z61yfnN3U4","media_key":"3_2037633242912935936"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037633244963737649"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T20:49:57.000Z","id":"2037633244963737649","author_id":"1595236921013407750","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":8},"text":"Anthropic has introduced a new feature that allows its chatbot Claude AI to directly use your computer to complete tasks. With this update, Claude can open apps, browse the web, and work with files.  Claude can do 'anything you'd do sitting at your desk.\n#News https://t.co/z61yfnN3U4"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037628262885580842"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T20:30:09.000Z","id":"2037628262885580842","author_id":"1784302397059162112","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":2,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":39},"text":"The Grokputer will come in and completely take over the “computer-use” industry directly pvping Claude and Openclaw\n\nThis will be huge when it drops\n\nDont be sidelined"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037615929220366840"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T19:41:09.000Z","id":"2037615929220366840","author_id":"1294641102369067008","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":28},"text":"Dev Catch Up #104 is here!\n\nGemini 3.1 Flash Live, Claude Computer Use, HF hf-mount, TurboQuant, SORA shutdown, LiteLLM security incident &amp; more.\n\nAll the key AI + dev updates in one place. https://t.co/C12ttD6YWf","entities":{"urls":[{"start":194,"end":217,"url":"https://t.co/C12ttD6YWf","expanded_url":"https://x.com/dev_shorts/status/2037615929220366840/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/C12ttD6YWf","media_key":"3_2037615898903851008"}]}},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037611409190867347"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T19:23:11.000Z","id":"2037611409190867347","author_id":"1749558738820751360","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"text":"Claude is moving beyond the chat box and straight onto your desktop.\n\nThis computer use feature is a massive step for AI. Imagine your assistant navigating Finder and Chrome to finish your tasks while you watch.\n\nThe permissions look intense but the potential is huge. We are https://t.co/2Z3Ivcf3PJ","entities":{"urls":[{"start":276,"end":299,"url":"https://t.co/2Z3Ivcf3PJ","expanded_url":"https://x.com/ricardotosatt/status/2037611409190867347/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/2Z3Ivcf3PJ","media_key":"3_2037611407370596352"}]}},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037606107988820320"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T19:02:07.000Z","id":"2037606107988820320","author_id":"1706086980008701953","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"text":"giving Claude an actual browser instead of screenshots is one of those changes that looks minor until you realize most 'computer use' failures were basically a resolution problem. raw pixels are a lossy interface for a model that can read the DOM directly"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037606077039333870"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T19:02:00.000Z","id":"2037606077039333870","author_id":"849801085204168705","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":13},"text":"\uD83E\uDD16 Claude Code em março ganhou /loop, Computer Use e 12 funcionalidades novas.\n\nO que muda na prática:\n1. /loop: pipelines agendados e repetitivos sem reabrir o terminal\n2. Computer Use: o agente enxerga a tela e interage como humano\n3. Multi-agent: orquestração de subagentes"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037599977468571785"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T18:37:46.000Z","id":"2037599977468571785","author_id":"1908017317818281984","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":30},"text":"\"2026 isn't the year of AI agents.\n\nIt's the year they start replacing entire engineering teams.\n\nClaude just built a working C compiler + Linux kernel contributions with minimal human input.\n\nGPT-5.4 Codex is doing real-time computer use.\n\nYour \"10x engineer\" is now a 100x agent"},{"entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":266,"end":269,"tag":"AI"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037591466374013318"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T18:03:56.000Z","id":"2037591466374013318","author_id":"2018406951936286720","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"text":"OpenAI's desktop superapp vs. Anthropic's computer-use Claude—we're officially in the 'Agentic Desktop' race. The OS is no longer the interface; the LLM is. If agents can manage your desktop, your workflow is about to become a single, long-running agentic loop. \uD83D\uDDA5️✨ #AI (1/2)"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037585707695251900"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T17:41:03.000Z","id":"2037585707695251900","author_id":"1225455010827374592","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":29},"text":"Test drove Claude Computer Use today and was impressed. Had it help me put together some slides for an upcoming keynote and encouraged live web browsing for researching data to fit my audience.\n\nUsage limits are brutal though, I’m sure Anthropic is running this at a loss but if"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037584397193323002","2037584610167517467"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T17:36:42.000Z","id":"2037584610167517467","author_id":"1959385998397435905","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":29},"text":"just another satisfying week in AI, buckle up:\n\nAnthropic shipped Computer Use — Claude now controls your Mac. mouse, keyboard, apps, everything. Phone Use coming next.\n\nClaude Code hit $2.5B in annualized revenue. Cursor at $2B. OpenAI Codex just crossed $1B. coding is the new"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037584397193323002","2037584610167517467"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T17:35:51.000Z","id":"2037584397193323002","author_id":"1959385998397435905","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":8},"text":"just another satisfying week in AI, buckle up:\n\nAnthropic shipped Computer Use — Claude now controls your Mac. mouse, keyboard, apps, everything. Phone Use coming next.\nClaude Code hit $2.5B in annualized revenue. Cursor at $2B. OpenAI Codex just crossed $1B. coding is the new"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037574970142798135"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T16:58:23.000Z","id":"2037574970142798135","author_id":"15627198","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":11},"text":"A Anthropic está claramente jogando uma partida diferente agora.\n\nClaude Cowork + Computer Use + Dispatch não é só mais feature. É um movimento de plataforma.\n\nEles não querem ser o chat que você usa. Querem ser o sistema onde você trabalha. (1/2)"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037569379366539746"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T16:36:10.000Z","id":"2037569379366539746","author_id":"1405031034","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":2,"like_count":3,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":1,"impression_count":390},"text":"This is actually insane...\n\nClaude can now use your computer from your phone \uD83E\uDD2F\n\nSo you send the job.\n\nThen walk away like a tiny CEO.\n\nIt does the work while you go touch grass.\n\nLink in the comments. https://t.co/HNjfXJcXLT","entities":{"urls":[{"start":201,"end":224,"url":"https://t.co/HNjfXJcXLT","expanded_url":"https://x.com/JulianGoldieSEO/status/2037569379366539746/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/HNjfXJcXLT","media_key":"3_2037569318750478337"}]}},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037567883606212767"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T16:30:14.000Z","id":"2037567883606212767","author_id":"1995490888886411264","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":41},"text":"I use OpenClaw and I love how powerful it is.\nBut right now, you still need to be okay with friction: installation, configuration, maintenance.\nWhat I see coming:\n• Perplexity is pushing this model with Perplexity Computer (an “agent on your computer” approach).\n• Claude is"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037560691586928759"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T16:01:39.000Z","id":"2037560691586928759","author_id":"765582","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":17},"text":"claude can now literally use your computer. point, click, scroll, open files, navigate your browser. assign it a task from your phone, go get coffee, come back to finished work.\n\nthis isn't a chatbot anymore. this is an employee.\n\nhttps://t.co/taXAMtTHNN","entities":{"urls":[{"start":231,"end":254,"url":"https://t.co/taXAMtTHNN","expanded_url":"https://claude.com/blog/dispatch-and-computer-use","display_url":"claude.com/blog/dispatch-…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2036206336741117952/LbvnasBF?format=jpg&name=orig","width":2000,"height":1000},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2036206336741117952/LbvnasBF?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Put Claude to work on your computer | Claude","description":"Claude now opens your apps, navigates your browser, and runs your dev tools to complete tasks. Assign from your phone with Dispatch. Research preview on macOS.","u